snippet.title: Haunted Memories Series Opening A
snippet.description:
Official opening for Haunted Memories game developed by Madman Theory Games (team members of ParanormalDev).

Official website: http://hauntedmemories.eu/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pages/Haunt-The-Real-Slender-Game/383858555029358
Steam Ep01 (FREE): http://store.steampowered.com/app/241640
Steam Ep02: http://store.steampowered.com/app/256280

PS - Hope you will enjoy new beginning of game known as "Haunt:TRSG" loooong time ago ;)
